prompt: Find all entities connected to John Doe
expected_response: MATCH (p:Person {name: 'John Doe'})-[r]-(connected) RETURN p, r, connected LIMIT 50

prompt: Show me all investigations from the last 30 days
expected_response: MATCH (i:Investigation) WHERE i.createdAt >= date() - duration('P30D') RETURN i ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC

prompt: Extract entities from: 'The meeting between CEO Alice Johnson and CFO Bob Smith took place at Acme Corp headquarters.'
Analyze the risk level of this relationship pattern
expected_response: Based on the relationship pattern analysis, this appears to be a medium-risk configuration with the following factors...

prompt: Find entities with more than 10 connections
expected_response: MATCH (n) WHERE size((n)--()) > 10 RETURN n, size((n)--()) as connections ORDER BY connections DESC LIMIT 25
